reviewText: Good flowing sequence. Doesn't keep you waiting through a lot of talking. Also like being able to custom tailor my workouts!
No fancy back drops or music.  Just plain and simple film style with quality exercises.  Love being able to customize my workout by level and length!

I really like this video.  A short demonstration is shown before each move and each then performed for 30 seconds.  It's simple and to the point, but a good workout.  Also, it's nice to have the option to choose the length of your workout.
